@startuml
title 비정상 흐름: 실패 요청 수만큼 Refresh 요청 중복 발생

actor User as U
participant "Frontend\n각 요청별 오류 처리" as FE
participant "Protected API" as API
participant "Auth API\n/refresh" as AUTH
database "Token Store" as STORE

U -> FE: 메뉴 진입
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data1\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data2\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data3\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data4\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data5\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data6\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data7\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/test/data8\nexpiredAccessToken

API --> FE: 401 data1
API --> FE: 401 data2
API --> FE: 401 data3
API --> FE: 401 data4
API --> FE: 401 data5
API --> FE: 401 data6
API --> FE: 401 data7
API --> FE: 401 data8

FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #1
FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #2
FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #3
FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #4
FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #5
FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #6
FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #7
FE -> AUTH: POST /refresh #8

AUTH -> STORE: Refresh Token 검증 반복
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken
AUTH --> FE: newAccessToken

note over FE,AUTH
문제점:
API 요청 8개가 실패했다고
Refresh 요청도 8회 발생한다.

이는 인증 서버, DB, Redis,
네트워크 부하를 불필요하게 증가시킨다.
end note

@enduml